83Storage::Record Entry::encodeAsStorageRecord() const
84{
85 WTF::Persistence::Encoder encoder;
86 encoder << m_response;
87
88 bool hasVaryingRequestHeaders = !m_varyingRequestHeaders.isEmpty();
89 encoder << hasVaryingRequestHeaders;
90 if (hasVaryingRequestHeaders)
91 encoder << m_varyingRequestHeaders;
92
93 bool isRedirect = !!m_redirectRequest;
94 encoder << isRedirect;
95 if (isRedirect)
96 m_redirectRequest->encodeWithoutPlatformData(encoder);
97
98 encoder << m_maxAgeCap;
99
100 encoder.encodeChecksum();
101
102 Data header(encoder.buffer(), encoder.bufferSize());
103 Data body;
104 if (m_buffer)
105 body = { m_buffer->data(), m_buffer->size() };
106
107 return { m_key, m_timeStamp, header, body, { } };
108}

110std::unique_ptr<Entry> Entry::decodeStorageRecord(const Storage::Record& storageEntry)
111{
112 auto entry = makeUnique<Entry>(storageEntry);
113
114 WTF::Persistence::Decoder decoder(storageEntry.header.data(), storageEntry.header.size());
115 WebCore::ResourceResponse response;
116 if (!WebCore::ResourceResponse::decode(decoder, response))
117 return nullptr;
118 entry->m_response = WTFMove(response);
119 entry->m_response.setSource(WebCore::ResourceResponse::Source::DiskCache);
120
121 std::optional<bool> hasVaryingRequestHeaders;
122 decoder >> hasVaryingRequestHeaders;
123 if (!hasVaryingRequestHeaders)
124 return nullptr;
125
126 if (*hasVaryingRequestHeaders) {
127 std::optional<Vector<std::pair<String, String>>> varyingRequestHeaders;
128 decoder >> varyingRequestHeaders;
129 if (!varyingRequestHeaders)
130 return nullptr;
131 entry->m_varyingRequestHeaders = WTFMove(*varyingRequestHeaders);
132 }
133
134 std::optional<bool> isRedirect;
135 decoder >> isRedirect;
136 if (!isRedirect)
137 return nullptr;
138
139 if (*isRedirect) {
140 entry->m_redirectRequest.emplace();
141 if (!entry->m_redirectRequest->decodeWithoutPlatformData(decoder))
142 return nullptr;
143 }
144
145 std::optional<std::optional<Seconds>> maxAgeCap;
146 decoder >> maxAgeCap;
147 if (!maxAgeCap)
148 return nullptr;
149 entry->m_maxAgeCap = WTFMove(*maxAgeCap);
150
151 if (!decoder.verifyChecksum()) {
152 LOG(NetworkCache, "(NetworkProcess) checksum verification failure\n");
153 return nullptr;
154 }
155
156 return entry;
157}
